ğŸ”¹ 3. ğ–ğ ğœğšğ§ ğğ§ğ­ğğ« ğ¯ğšğ¥ğ®ğğ¬ ğğ®ğ«ğ¢ğ§ğ  ğ«ğ®ğ§ğ­ğ¢ğ¦ğ

 If variables are not provided, Terraform will interactively ask for them.
 This is good for manual execution but not recommended for automation.

We can choose any method based on the use case â€” but for real projects, .ğ­ğŸğ¯ğšğ«ğ¬ ğšğ§ğ ğšğ®ğ­ğ¨ğ¦ğšğ­ğ¢ğ¨ğ§ ğ¯ğ¢ğš ğ‚ğˆ/ğ‚ğƒ ğ©ğ¢ğ©ğğ¥ğ¢ğ§ğğ¬ are the most reliable and scalable options.

